# Hostinger Node.js Web App - .htaccess (optional)
# This file is typically not needed for Node.js Web Apps on Hostinger
# as they handle routing through their Node.js environment.
# However, if you need specific redirects, you can add them here.

# Example: Redirect HTTP to HTTPS (if not handled automatically)
# RewriteEngine On
# RewriteCond %{HTTPS} off
# RewriteRule ^(.*)$ https://%{HTTP_HOST}%{REQUEST_URI} [L,R=301]
